48:07.620 --> 48:13.480
From that physical foundation, we followed the structure-preserving functor into the human mind.

48:14.160 --> 48:19.840
We saw how our cognition utilizes that exact same mathematical projection.

48:20.320 --> 48:26.280
We tried to stitch local, consistent cognitive tiles into a global understanding.

