We fundamentally redefined ourselves.

48:53.820 --> 48:55.580
We are not static dots on a server.

48:55.760 --> 48:58.800
We are dynamic, unbroken historical trajectories.

48:59.260 --> 49:03.120
And we saw the mathematical proof of why digital platforms become toxic.

